Pre-Game Insights: Bhutan and Indonesia will lock horns in the 6th T20I of Quadrangular T20I Series in Bhutan 2024 on Tuesday, 22 October 2024, at Gelephu International Cricket Ground, Gelephu.
Bhutan’s Predicted Playing XI includes Tshering Tashi, Ranjung Mikyo Dorji, Tenjin Rabgey, etc.
Indonesia’s Predicted Playing XI includes Ahmad Ramdoni (WK), Dharma Kadek Kesuma, Anjar Tadarus, etc.
